Cardinality assertions are expressed explicitly through statements in KB, \fact{Marie Curie}{numberOfChildren}{2}, and in text, \textit{``Curie \underline{won 37 awards} in her lifetime''}. Correctly identified, such statements allow for a direct numeric evaluation of KB recall.